sire, and failure in which hope for the future gets lost in the tragic comedy of power.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mrz 2022) 0aColonial administratorszCameroonvBiography. 0aColonial administratorszFrancevBiography. 0aMedical ethicsxColonieszFrancexHistoryy20th century. 0aMedical ethicszCameroonxHistoryy20th century. 0aMedical ethicszFrancexColoniesxHistoryy20th century. 0aMedicinexColonieszFrancexHistoryy20th century. 0aMedicinezCameroonxHistoryy20th century. 0aMedicinezFrancexColoniesxHistoryy20th century. 0aPhysicianszCameroonvBiography. 0aPhysicianszFrancevBiography. 7aHISTORY / Africa / Central.2bisacsh1 aSmeall, Cheryl.40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781478022480423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781478022480/original  aEBA_DUK_ALL  aEBA_DUK_EALL  aEBA_DUK_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles